These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
House: craftsman, futuristic, art-deco
3 different pets are kept: lizard, snake, goldfish
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, july, october
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, dannemann, havana
City: berlin, rome, boston
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, lily, poppy
There are 3 different favourite colors: amber, blood-red, blue
 1. the person who likes amber is the person who growslily##1
 2. the person who likes blue is the havana-smoker##1
 3. the art-deco house is between the person who growspoppy and the futuristic house##2
 4. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 5. the dannemann-smoker is the owner of the goldfish##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 8. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 9. the person who likes amber is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| House      | futuristic    | art-deco   | craftsman           |
| Pet          | snake       | goldfish    | lizard         |
| Birthday         | july    | october  | december        |
| Cigar           | siglo | dannemann   | havana      |
| City   | rome        | boston    | berlin       |
| Flower   | lily     | daffodil  | poppy       |
| Color         | amber     | blood-red | blue |

