3 different games are played: canasta, bridge, poker
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, december, august
House: townhouse, art-deco, palace
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, pink, red
 1. the palace house is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 2. the palace house is the software-developer##1
 3. the software-developer is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 4. the person who likes blood-red is between the person traveling to paris and the person traveling to marseilles##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1
 6. the person traveling to paris is the person playing canasta##1
 7. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who likes red##1
 8. the vegafina-smoker is the architect##1
 9. the software-developer is on the right of the person playing poker##1
10. the palace house is on the left of the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| City      | marseilles   | berlin    | paris         |
| Cigar          | vegafina    | havana | cain          |
| Job   | architect  | software-developer  | pilot     |
| Game   | poker       | bridge      | canasta         |
