 6. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 7. the person drinking tea is between the person who growsrose and the analyst##2
 8. the person who growsrose is on the left of the dressmaker##1
 9. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
10. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
11. the person who growsrose is the bongani-smoker##1

