.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-17::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, black, brown
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, musician, writer
House: modern, gothic-revival, tower
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, april, january
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, punk, house
3 different games are played: chess, mah-jongg, poker
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, ritmeester, montecristo
 1. the person playing poker is in the middle##1
 2. the person who likes black is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the electrician##1
 4. the writer is the gothic-revival house##1
 5. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 6. the fan house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 7. the montecristo-smoker is between the person who likes emerald and the person who's birthday is in july##2
 8. the modern house is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 9. the gothic-revival house is the alhambra-smoker##1
10. the fan house is on the left of the fan punk##1
11. the alhambra-smoker is the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Color      | emerald | black      | brown      |
| Job         | electrician     | musician     | writer  |
| House   | tower | modern  | gothic-revival |
| Birthday   | april  | january     | july |
| Music-Genre           | jazz        | house | punk     |
| Game         | chess    | poker | mah-jongg   |
| Cigar     | ritmeester        | montecristo        | alhambra   |

