.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, rose, tulip
3 different pets are kept: mouse, hedgehog, guinea-pig
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, montecristo, aristoff
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, lavender, ebony
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, colombian, indian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, january, may
House: tower, craftsman, futuristic
1. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
2. the futuristic house is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is between the brazilian and the person who likes lavender##2
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person who likes ebony and the aristoff-smoker##2
6. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
8. the tower house is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
9. the colombian is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Flower      | balloon-flower      | rose      | tulip       |
| Pet          | hedgehog      | guinea-pig    | mouse   |
| Cigar         | aristoff    | alhambra     | montecristo     |
| Color           | lavender    | fuchsia | ebony   |
| Nationality   | colombian    | indian    | brazilian       |
| Birthday         | may | february      | january    |
| House     | craftsman       | tower | futuristic |

