.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-19::.
City: prague, colone, berlin
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, november, october
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, lavender, yellow
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, dutch, australian
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, lily, aconite
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, lawyer, dancer
3 different games are played: whist, mah-jongg, poker
1. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who likes lavender##1
2. the lawyer is on the right of the japanese##1
3. the dancer is on the right of the lawyer##1
4. the australian is on the right of the person playing poker##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person traveling to berlin and the person who likes emerald##2
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
7. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person who growslily##1
8. the person playing whist is the australian##1
9. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| City      | berlin       | prague     | colone         |
| Birthday          | march     | november      | october     |
| Color         | lavender | yellow    | emerald      |
| Nationality   | japanese   | dutch | australian    |
| Flower   | lily        | aconite     | poppy   |
| Job         | mechanic     | lawyer | dancer |
| Game     | mah-jongg     | poker       | whist    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, blend, siglo
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, spy, western
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, reading, collecting
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, tulip, rose
3 different games are played: chess, snooker, canasta
House: palace, art-deco, colonial
City: colone, marseilles, berlin
1. the prince-smoker is the person watching western movies##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is the palace house##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the siglo-smoker and the person playing canasta##2
4. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
5. the person playing chess is on the left of the colonial house##1
6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
7. the person who's hobby is reading is the person watching adventure movies##1
8. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing chess##1
9. the person who growstulip is between the person watching adventure movies and the person traveling to colone##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Cigar      | blend    | prince       | siglo      |
| Movie-Genre          | adventure   | western   | spy  |
| Hobby           | reading  | fishing | collecting    |
| Flower   | iris   | tulip     | rose  |
| Game           | canasta     | chess        | snooker |
| House         | art-deco | palace   | colonial  |
| City     | marseilles    | berlin     | colone      |

 